pmnch-subtext: Barka da zuwa "Abin da Matasa ke So" Dashboard! Wannan kayan aikin haɗin gwiwar yana ba da wakilci na gani na martani da fahimtar da muke tattarawa daga matasa masu shekaru 10-24 a duniya. Jigon shirin shine tambaya mai buɗewa: "Don inganta jin daɗina, ina so...". Matasa daga ko'ina cikin duniya suna amsa wannan, suna ba mu haske na musamman game da buƙatunsu, fatansu, da burinsu. Bincika bayanan, gano labaran da ke bayan lambobi, kuma ku kasance tare da mu don faɗaɗa muryoyin matasa biliyan 1.8 a duniya. Don ƙarin koyo game da yaƙin neman zaɓe, ziyarci http://www.1point8.org.
